  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_be_pattern",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 4,
    "__type": "paragraph",
    "text": "If the question uses \"to be\" (am, is, are), put \"to be\" first, then the subject (person or pronoun)."
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_be_examples",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 5,
    "__type": "table",
    "__headers": [
      { "text": "Pattern", "__type": "text" },
      { "text": "Question", "__type": "text" }
    ],
    "__entries": [
      { "__type": "text", "text": "\"to be\" + subject" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Are you a student?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "\"to be\" + subject" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Is she at home?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "\"to be\" + subject" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Are they ready?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "\"to be\" + subject" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Is the weather cold?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "\"to be\" + subject" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Are we late?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "\"to be\" + subject" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Is he your friend?" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_be_short_answers_header",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 6,
    "__type": "subheader",
    "text": "Positive Short Answers with \"To Be\""
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_yes_carousel",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 6.5,
    "__type": "vocabularyCarousel",
    "__words": ["yes"]
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_be_short_answers_positive",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 7,
    "__type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Say \"Yes, I am\" or \"Yes, she is.\" Do not use contractions in the positive answer."
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_be_short_answers_positive_table",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 8,
    "__type": "table",
    "__headers": [
      { "text": "Question", "__type": "text" },
      { "text": "Correct Short Answer", "__type": "text" },
      { "text": "❌Incorrect", "__type": "text" }
    ],
    "__entries": [
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Are you a student?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Yes, I am.\nYes, I am a student." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "❌Yes, I'm." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Is she at home?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Yes, she is.\nYes, she is at home." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "❌Yes, she's." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Are they ready?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Yes, they are.\nYes, they are ready." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "❌Yes, they're." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Is the weather cold?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Yes, it is.\nYes, it is cold." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "❌Yes, it's." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Are we late?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Yes, we are.\nYes, we are late." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "❌Yes, we're." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Is he your friend?" },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "Yes, he is.\nYes, he is my friend." },
      { "__type": "text", "text": "❌Yes, he's." }
    ]
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_be_short_answers_negative_header",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 9,
    "__type": "subheader",
    "text": "Negative Short Answers with \"To Be\""
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_no_carousel",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 9.2,
    "__type": "vocabularyCarousel",
    "__words": ["no", "not"]
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_be_short_answers_negative_paragraph",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 9.5,
    "__type": "paragraph",
    "text": "For negative short answers, you can say \"No, I'm not\" or \"No, she isn't.\" You can use \"is not\" or \"isn't\". Both are correct."
  },

  {
