    "text": "Yes/No Questions with Other Verbs"
  },
  {
    "_id": "yes_no_questions_other_verbs_pattern",
    "__lessons": ["yes or no questions"],
    "__order": 12,
    "__type": "paragraph",
    "text": "If the question does not use \"to be,\" start with \"do\" or \"does.\" Use \"do\" for I, you, we, they. Use \"does\" for he, she, it."
  },
  {
